      <text xml:space="preserve">{{about|a language developed at Bell Labs|“B” language of Meertens and Pemberton|ABC (programming language)|another meanings|B (disambiguation)#Computing and internet}}
{{morefootnotes|date=May 2009}}
{{Infobox programming language
| name                   = B
| logo                   =
| caption                =
| file_ext               =
| paradigm               =
| year                   = 1969
| designer               = [[Ken Thompson (computer programmer)|Ken Thompson]]
| developer              = [[Ken Thompson (computer programmer)|Ken Thompson]], [[Dennis Ritchie]]
