==General Concept==
===Ecology and evolution===
*'''[[Life]]''': [[origin of life]] — [[hierarchy of life]] - [[Miller-Urey experiment]]
*'''[[Ecology]]''':
**[[Autecology]]: [[autotroph]] — [[heterotroph]] — [[acclimatization]] — [[Warm-blooded|endotherm]] — [[ectotherm]] — [[hibernation]] — [[homeostasis]] — [[behavior]] — [[circadian rhythm]]
