**[[Ecosystems]]: [[biodiversity]] — [[biome]] — [[habitat (ecology)|habitat]] — [[plankton]] — [[thermocline]] — [[carbon cycle]] — [[water cycle]] — [[nitrogen cycle]] — [[food web]] — [[trophic level]] — [[saprobe]] — [[decomposition]]
